author: Alice O'Malley
title: Alice O'Malley
text: I was buying a gift for my friend who was expecting twins. The twins arrive d into the world a little early and I was out of the country. Not a problem for the customer service support team, who ensured that my gifts were delivered free to my friend while I was away. Thank you
